                  <h2 style="margin-left: 20px">I can't believe we still put up with this!</h2>
                  <p style="padding: 20px">The age of mass travel has arrived. Today it is estimated that over 2 billion cross border tourists ply the planet. Being constantly on the move has led us all to experience a new, uncomfortable and unhealthy environment – resting and sleeping in a seat. Seats were not designed for this purpose and neither were we.
                     Pillows, cushions and neck supports don’t address the CORE problem – gravity. 
                     Time for a change?
                  </p>
                  <br><br>
                  <div class="exhibitior-main-img">
                     <a target="_blank" href="http://britishinventionshow.com/uploads/concept_bag_3x3_1413399712.jpg"><img src="http://britishinventionshow.com/uploads/concept_bag_3x3_1413399712.jpg" style=""></a>
